# MERIT Docker build context
#
# The repository working tree contains multiple historical caches, manuscript
# artifacts, screenshots, and release folders. The public Docker image should
# package only the current UI runtime. It must not bundle the Workbench v7 cache
# or local raw/source data dumps.

*

!merit-ui-v2/
!merit-ui-v2/api/
!merit-ui-v2/api/**
!merit-ui-v2/merit/
!merit-ui-v2/merit/**
!merit-ui-v2/static/
!merit-ui-v2/static/**
!merit-ui-v2/Logo.png
!merit-ui-v2/README.md
!merit-ui-v2/pyproject.toml
!merit-ui-v2/requirements.txt

!docker/
!docker/**
!docker-compose.merit.yml
